<TEXT>
the son of a slain hollywood 
executive was arrested thursday in the shotgun slayings of his 
parents and his teenage brother was being sought in israel 
authorities said 
lyle menendez 22 was charged with two counts of murder in the 
deaths of jose menendez 45 and his wife mary louise kitty 
menendez 44 said deputy district attorney elden fox 
menendez 19yearold brother erik was named in the complaint 
and was being sought in israel on identical counts fox said 
police would not reveal a motive but ruled out earlier 
speculation that drugs or organized crime were involved police 
chief marvin iannone said physical evidence linked the aug 20 
killings to the sons whom he described as the triggermen 
i dont know if there was one motive or several iannone 
said as in any family there are a lot of conflicts who knows 
what really goes on in families 
the focus became very clear over the past few months that the 
sons did it iannone said we were just waiting for the glue 
binding it together 
he declined to elaborate on information that led to the arrests 
jose menendez was chairman of live entertainment inc a video 
and music distribution business affiliated with carolco pictures 
inc producers of the rambo movies 
under terms of the parents 9yearold wills the sons share a 
10 million estate they also were beneficiaries of a 400000 life 
insurance policy 
the complaint includes specialcircumstances allegations that 
make the sons eligible for the death penalty if convicted 
the couple were killed by multiple shotgun blasts at close 
range their sons who reported the killings said they found the 
bodies after a night out 
in the months after the killings lyle menendez traveled the 
country making investments and buying stores particularly 
fastfood franchises said iannone 
lyle menendez was arrested at 120 pm as he was preparing to 
drive away from the family mansion he had been under surveillance 
for the past 36 hours iannone said 
erik menendez was believed to be taking part in a tennis 
tournament in israel police were seeking help from the state 
department the israeli government and interpol the international 
police organization 
at the time of the shootings nothing was stolen from the 
spanishstyle 5 million home there were no signs the killers 
forced their way in and reportedly no clues at the scene 
police said during the investigation that they were looking into 
the disappearance of a computerized record concerning menendezs 
plans to write a new will 
family members speaking four months after the slayings on 
condition of anonymity said a relative tried to read a computer 
file named will after the murders but was unable to do so 
before a computer expert was brought in the file disappeared 
the relatives would not say who might have erased the file 
iannone declined to comment in detail except to say the will 
was very much involved in our investigation 
the elder menendez had little money when his parents sent him 
from cuba after castro took power he was an executive for rca and 
hertz before joining live entertainment 
companies operated by live had been linked to organized crime 
and pornography before live bought them but company officials have 
rejected suggestions the deaths may have a mob link 
</TEXT>
