everywhere from evening gowns to parkas 
genny suits featuring the same length for the jacket and the 
hemline of the skirt 
krizia lots of comfortable winter shorts and cozy sweater 
dresses 
missoni reversible quilted duffel coat with a multicolored 
knit print from russian folklore 
moschino a runway ballet show instead of a fashion show with 
dancers haphazardly donning clothes over skincolored leotards to 
decry the state of fashion and its mega shows 
mario valentino beautiful bright tricolored shearlings 
versace micromini skirts and the new 1990 aline silhouette 
