up 30223 points or 090 percent it gained 32855 points thursday 
the dollar closed at 15115 yen up 032 yen it started trading 
friday at 15107 yen and ranged between 15100 and 15140 yen 
yields on benchmark no 119 10year government bonds were quoted 
at 7170 percent at 3 pm down from 7205 percent at the markets 
closing thursday 
