minority said in appealing for broader minority representation 
we were about 100000 we lived in romania for many centuries 
after the dictatorship only 7000 remained if you dont vote for 
us to get a seat that means that you deny our role as martyrs 
much of the nations armenian population perished in stalinist 
labor camps after world war ii 
the draft law provides for a mixture of direct election of 
candidates and proportional representation to reflect geographical 
regions as well as the more than 50 parties 
most of them are small groupings that have sprung up in the 
aftermath of the december revolution which ended ceausescus 
24year stalinist rule 
