series based on bagdad cafe but declined whoopi goldberg 
plays the role in the series 
i may do another series but i felt i had done bagdad 
cafe she said if i had done it i would have done it just 
for the money brendas walking a very thin line on being just your 
basic handsonloudmouth it could become shallow in a series if 
you dont have good writing 
